[h3 id=UnknownLoadErrorOccurredTroubleshooting 
	""Unknown load error occurred" Troubleshooting
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Using Bizhawk 2.9.1, this was seen when attempting to run a Hyper Neo Geo 64 game "Fatal Fury: Wild Ambition".  As of now Hyper Neo Geo 64 does not work. 
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"The seven Hyper Neo Geo 64 games list: 
		[a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyper_Neo_Geo_64 rel=noopener external nofollow 
			"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyper_Neo_Geo_64
		]a
